Bundled GTDB taxonomy data notice
================================

This repository contains two different licence regimes.

Project code and packaging metadata for `gtdb-genomes` are provided under the
MIT licence in `LICENSE`.

Published distribution archives bundle GTDB taxonomy data under
`data/gtdb_taxonomy/<release>/*.tsv.gz` for runtime use and package tests. The
source repository tracks only `data/gtdb_taxonomy/releases.tsv`, and source
checkouts generate the release payload directories during bootstrap. The GTDB
taxonomy data is not relicensed by this project.

Attribution for the bundled GTDB taxonomy data:
- source: Genome Taxonomy Database (GTDB)
- bootstrap mirror: https://data.ace.uq.edu.au/public/gtdb/data/releases/
- applicable licence: Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
- licence URL: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/
- included licence text: licenses/CC-BY-SA-4.0.txt

The bundled GTDB taxonomy payload shipped in built distribution archives is
generated from the recorded UQ mirror release sources and checksum listings.
Users redistributing or adapting those files must comply with the applicable
CC BY-SA 4.0 terms, attribution requirements, and any downstream ShareAlike
obligations.
